28 Chapter 9.5. Expungement and Sealing of Conviction Records
29 Sec. 1. (a) This chapter applies to an expungement petition filed
30 after June 30, 2026.
31 (b) This chapter does not apply to:
32 (1) a person who has been convicted of:
