28 under this chapter as part of a plea agreement. Any purported
29 waiver of the right to expungement in a plea agreement is invalid
30 and unenforceable as against public policy.
31 (b) This section does not prohibit the finding of a waiver of the
32 right to expungement based on a failure to comply with the
33 provisions of this chapter.
